      "writtenOn": "2021-03-25T00:53:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think run event will only sent when queue gets rate limited and decides to put it in waitlist first but not when a slot can be acquired right away.\n\nI will add the test when I implement rate limit functionalities.\n\nOr do you mean we should send the event regardless?",
